text: Sir Iakoba Taeia Italeli, GCMG, is a Tuvaluan politician. He was the Governor- General of Tuvalu from 16 April 2010 until 22 August 2019."New Tuvaluan MPs get key cabinet portfolios", Pacific Islands News Association, 29 September 2010 He is also a former Attorney General of Tuvalu who served from 2002 to 2006. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Governors-General of Tuvalu
